statistics <- list(
  ' ' = ~length(.x) %>% as.character(),
  #' ( )' = ~sum(!is.na(.x)) %>% as.character(),
  ' ' = ~sum(is.na(.x)) %>% as.character(),
  '. .' = ~ifelse(sum(!is.na(.x)) == 0, "/", mean(.x, na.rm = TRUE) %>% round(2) %>% as.character()),
  '. .' = ~ifelse(sum(!is.na(.x)) < 2, "/", sd(.x, na.rm = TRUE) %>% round(2)) %>% as.character(),
  '95%   ' = ~ifelse(sum(!is.na(.x)) < 2, "/", 
                                {mean <- mean(.x, na.rm = TRUE)
                                  se <- sd(.x, na.rm = TRUE) / sqrt(sum(!is.na(.x)))
                                  lower_ci <- mean - 1.96 * se
                                  upper_ci <- mean + 1.96 * se
                                  paste0(round(lower_ci, 2), " - ", round(upper_ci, 2))} %>% as.character()),
  '. - .' = ~ifelse(sum(!is.na(.x)) == 0, "/", paste0(min(.x, na.rm = TRUE) %>% round(2), " - ", max(.x, na.rm = TRUE) %>% round(2))) %>% as.character(),
  '' = ~ifelse(sum(!is.na(.x)) == 0, "/", median(.x, na.rm = TRUE) %>% round(2) %>% as.character()),
  'Q1 - Q3' = ~ifelse(sum(!is.na(.x)) == 0, "/", paste0(quantile(.x, 0.25, na.rm = TRUE) %>% round(2), " - ", quantile(.x, 0.75, na.rm = TRUE) %>% round(2))) %>% as.character(),
  'IQR' = ~ifelse(sum(!is.na(.x)) == 0, "/", IQR(.x, na.rm = TRUE) %>% round(2) %>% as.character())
)

cleaned_data_factors <- cleaned_data %>%
  select(where(is.factor), -`Unique id`) %>%
  pivot_longer(-`Stroke event`, names_to = "Variable", values_to = "Category") %>%
  count(`Stroke event`, Variable, Category) %>%
  group_by(`Stroke event`, Variable) %>%
  mutate('  (%)' = round(n / sum(n) * 100, 1)) %>% 
  mutate('95% ' = paste0(round((n / sum(n) - 1.96 * sqrt((n / sum(n) * (1 - n / sum(n))) / sum(n))) * 100, 1), " - ", round((n / sum(n) + 1.96 * sqrt((n / sum(n) * (1 - n / sum(n))) / sum(n))) * 100, 1))) %>%
  rename(' ' = n) %>%
  flextable() %>%
  theme_box() %>%
  align(align = "center", part = "all") %>%
  merge_v(c("Stroke event", "Variable"))

create_pie_chart <- function(df) {
  hchart(df, "pie", hcaes(x = Category, y = count), name = unique(df$Variable)) %>%
    hc_title(text = unique(df$Variable), style = list(fontSize = '14px', fontWeight = 'bold')) %>%
    hc_plotOptions(pie = list(dataLabels = list(enabled = TRUE, format = '{point.percentage:.1f}%', distance = -30), showInLegend = TRUE))
}
